title: TrickBot
extract: Trickbot is basically a Trojan which can infect your computer system severely. Trickbot usually attacks banking sites by inserting a malicious code or content in those site. ... Trickbot was first detected in a threat campaign targeting computer users in Australia in the September 2016.
